<h3>Home (Main) Page Configuration</h3>

<p>You can choose one of the two available page layouts.</p>

In order to configure the second main page layout you need to add static blocks from <strong>sources -> demo -> static_blocks</strong> folder and apply them using widgets. 
<p>To find out how to add static blocks and apply them using widgets, check the following section <strong>Magento theme installation -> Static blocks configuration</strong>. The following <strong><a href="http://livedemo00.template-help.com/magento_53638/template-settings" target="blank_">Template settings</a></strong> table and the image below will be also useful. 
